Examples

Below are some examples to illustrate the possibilities and extensive configurability of twyg. All examples were generated by simply combining the built-in configurations and colorschemes. Every built-in configuration is shown with three different colorschemes.

You can recreate all images on this page by running the script docs/examples/generate-samples.sh in the distribution package. The example JSON data can be found in the example-data directory.
